      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>如果抛开沪港通机制，从更广义角度看近十年QFII的偏好来看。海外资金进入中国后，其持仓偏好可以归结为以下几个特征：</span></p>
            <section style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</section>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(189, 77, 13); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>1. 高股息率；</span></strong></span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(189, 77, 13); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>2. 大市值（200~500亿以上）；</span></strong></span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(189, 77, 13); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>3. 较低市盈率（20X以下的持仓达75%）</span></strong></span></p>
          </section>
